T02D2855:196a-4: dpal 'jig rten dbang phyug la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2855:196a-5: mi rtag sdug bsngal dran byas nas //
T02D2855:196a-6: snying rje chen po rab bskyed de //
T02D2855:196a-7: spyi bor bla ma snying gar lha //
T02D2855:196a-8: rang sems ma yengs bsgom par bya //
T02D2855:196a-9: gang shar thams cad de yin te //
T02D2855:196a-10: de ni gang du'ang ma shar ba'o //
T02D2855:196a-11: de phyir gang skyes de ma skyes //
T02D2855:196a-12: ma skyes pa nyid skye ba'i tshul //
T02D2855:196a-13: gang skyes gnyug ma nyid yin phyir //
T02D2855:196a-14: de shar dran pas ma brjed na //
T02D2855:196a-15: gang snang stong pa nyid bdag tu //
T02D2855:196a-16: rnal 'byor rgyal por gdon mi za //
T02D2855:196a-17: ma rtogs 'gro la rang dbang du //
T02D2855:196a-18: rnam kun dmigs pa med yid kyis //
T02D2855:196a-19: snying rje chen po ngang gis 'grub //
T02D2855:196a-20: de yi thabs sbyangs byang chub bzhed //
T02D2855:196a-21: rnal 'byor snying po rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen
